System requirements:
==========================

Bounty Hunter: Black Dawn - that's over a dynamic first-person shooter. Look forward to a long and interesting journey into the world of fighting. In the game you will come across a large number of weapons, quests, and powerups. You have the choice will be 8 adventurers with different skills and attributes. Landscapes of the game is very interesting, and the storyline is imbued with humor.

3) Play!
